---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Research" description="Ismail El Jamiy's PhD research on Handwritten Text Recognition of medieval Arabic scientific manuscripts and dedicated LLMs.">

  <article class="page-container">

    <header class="page-header">
      <div class="page-eyebrow">PhD Research</div>
      <h1 class="page-title">Research</h1>
      <div class="page-rule-short" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <p class="page-subtitle">
        <span class="page-badge">PhD in AI · 2025–2028</span>
        &ensp;University of Toulouse (IRIT / IMT / CLLE)
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose">

      <p class="drop-cap">
        The Arabic scientific tradition carries eight centuries of knowledge in astronomy, algebra,
        and medicine. My PhD makes these manuscripts computationally accessible, beginning with
        al-Bīrūnī's <em>al-Qānūn al-Mas'ūdī</em> (written c. 1030) as a first corpus.
      </p>

      <!-- ── Challenges ──────────────────────────────── -->
      <h2>What makes this hard</h2>
      <div class="challenge-grid">

        <div class="challenge-card">
          <div class="challenge-icon">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Calligraphic diversity</h3>
          <p>Six copies, six hands. Each scribe used a distinct style with elongation strokes and unique ligatures.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="challenge-card">
          <div class="challenge-icon">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 1v4M12 19v4M4.22 4.22l2.83 2.83M16.95 16.95l2.83 2.83M1 12h4M19 12h4M4.22 19.78l2.83-2.83M16.95 7.05l2.83-2.83"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Scientific vocabulary</h3>
          <p>Astronomical and mathematical terms absent from any modern Arabic training corpus.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="challenge-card">
          <div class="challenge-icon">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="9" y="9" width="13" height="13" rx="2"/><path d="M5 15H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Eight centuries of copying</h3>
          <p>The same text survives in copies from the 12th to the 19th century. Models must generalise across all of them.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="challenge-card">
          <div class="challenge-icon">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="9.5" y1="15.5" x2="14.5" y2="15.5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Document wear</h3>
          <p>Water stains, faded ink, marginal annotations and physical damage introduce significant noise.</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- ── Pipeline ────────────────────────────────── -->
      <h2>The pipeline</h2>
      <div class="pipeline" role="img" aria-label="Research pipeline: manuscript image to searchable text">
        <div class="pipe-step">
          <div class="pipe-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"/><polyline points="21 15 16 10 5 21"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="pipe-label">Manuscript<br>image</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pipe-arrow" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pipe-step">
          <div class="pipe-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="pipe-label">HTR<br>model</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pipe-arrow" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pipe-step">
          <div class="pipe-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="pipe-label">Arabic<br>transcription</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pipe-arrow" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pipe-step">
          <div class="pipe-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="pipe-label">Medieval<br>Arabic LLM</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ── Approach tabs ───────────────────────────── -->
      <h2>My approach</h2>
      <div class="approach-tabs" role="tablist">
        <button class="approach-tab active" role="tab" aria-selected="true"  data-panel="0"><span class="tab-num">01</span>Dataset</button>
        <button class="approach-tab"        role="tab" aria-selected="false" data-panel="1"><span class="tab-num">02</span>Language models</button>
        <button class="approach-tab"        role="tab" aria-selected="false" data-panel="2"><span class="tab-num">03</span>Pipeline</button>
      </div>
      <div class="approach-panels">
        <div class="approach-panel active" id="panel-0" role="tabpanel">
          <strong>ATHAAR</strong> is the first manually annotated benchmark for medieval Arabic scientific manuscript recognition. It compiles 1,031 lines from six witnesses of al-Bīrūnī's <em>al-Qānūn</em>, spanning the 12th to 19th century, held at institutions including the Bibliothèque nationale de France and the British Library.
        </div>
        <div class="approach-panel" id="panel-1" role="tabpanel">
          Once text is recognised, the goal is language models pre-trained on medieval Arabic scientific prose. Standard Arabic LLMs struggle with archaic vocabulary and domain-specific terminology. A dedicated model enables accurate translation, semantic search, and scholarly indexing.
        </div>
        <div class="approach-panel" id="panel-2" role="tabpanel">
          Beyond models, the goal is a usable tool: historians submit a manuscript image and get a searchable, correctable transcription. Accessibility for non-technical scholars is a first-class requirement.
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ── Institutions ────────────────────────────── -->
      <div class="inst-row">
        <span class="inst-tag">IRIT</span>
        <span class="inst-tag">IMT</span>
        <span class="inst-tag">CLLE</span>
        <span class="inst-text">University of Toulouse · 2025–2028</span>
      </div>

    </div>
  </article>

</BaseLayout>

<script>
  const tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.approach-tab');
  const panels = document.querySelectorAll('.approach-panel');

  tabs.forEach(tab => {
    tab.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const idx = tab.dataset.panel;
      tabs.forEach(t => { t.classList.remove('active'); t.setAttribute('aria-selected', 'false'); });
      panels.forEach(p => p.classList.remove('active'));
      tab.classList.add('active');
      tab.setAttribute('aria-selected', 'true');
      document.getElementById(`panel-${idx}`)?.classList.add('active');
    });
  });
</script>

<style>
  .page-container {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem 5rem;
  }

  .page-header { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }

  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--fg);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Prose ─────────────────────────────────────── */
  .prose {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--fg);
  }

  .prose p { margin-bottom: 1.3em; }

  .prose h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-olive);
    margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .drop-cap::first-letter {
    font-size: 4.5em;
    line-height: 0.78;
    float: left;
    margin-right: 0.08em;
    color: var(--color-terracotta);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
  }

  /* ── Challenge grid ─────────────────────────────── */
  .challenge-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .challenge-card {
    background: var(--bg-panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.25rem 1rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    cursor: default;
  }

  .challenge-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: var(--color-olive);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-olive) 10%, transparent);
  }

  .challenge-icon {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-terracotta) 10%, transparent);
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    color: var(--color-terracotta);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .challenge-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    color: var(--fg);
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
  }

  .challenge-card p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.83rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Pipeline ───────────────────────────────────── */
  .pipeline {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0;
    background: var(--bg-panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    row-gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .pipe-step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    min-width: 80px;
    transition: transform 0.15s;
  }

  .pipe-step:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .pipe-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-olive) 10%, transparent);
    border: 1.5px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-olive) 25%, transparent);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-olive);
    transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .pipe-step:hover .pipe-icon {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-olive) 18%, transparent);
    border-color: var(--color-olive);
  }

  .pipe-label {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }

  .pipe-arrow {
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    opacity: 0.4;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin: 0 0.25rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.4rem;
  }

  /* ── Approach tabs ──────────────────────────────── */
  .approach-tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .approach-tab {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.55rem 1rem;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    margin-bottom: -2px;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: color 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .approach-tab:hover { color: var(--fg); }

  .approach-tab.active {
    color: var(--color-olive);
    border-bottom-color: var(--color-olive);
  }

  .tab-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .approach-panels {
    background: var(--bg-panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-top: none;
    border-radius: 0 0 0.5rem 0.5rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .approach-panel {
    display: none;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--fg);
  }

  .approach-panel.active { display: block; }

  /* ── Institutions ───────────────────────────────── */
  .inst-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .inst-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-olive) 10%, transparent);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-olive) 22%, transparent);
    color: var(--color-olive);
  }

  .inst-text {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
  }

  /* ── Responsive ─────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .challenge-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }

    .pipeline {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .pipe-arrow {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
      padding-bottom: 0;
      align-self: center;
    }

    .approach-tabs { overflow-x: auto; }
  }
</style>
